headline: Agilent to Participate in Jefferies Global Healthcare Conference
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif, May 15, 2025--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) today announced that CEO Padraig McDonnell — along with CFO Bob McMahon — will participate in a fireside chat at the Jefferies Global Healthcare Conference at 10:30 a.m. Eastern on Wednesday, June 4, 2025, in New York City.
